	<!-- Merge Cohesion!  The items above form a hierarchy which we compress to
			the approx. minimum possible depth that still avoids needing to scroll
			on any given screen.
			Normally we work top-to-bottom, depth-first, when performing this merge.
			However, for certain items (e.g. "how to play") we prefer to keep the
			node cohesive as long as possible.  We only merge menu items into their
			parent if their parent has >= their cohesion, or the items will
			be fully contained within their own category. -->
